head into autumn and winter.<\/p>\n<p>If you\u2019re on the hunt for a first-class location caterer for a TV show or film, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/contact-us\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">get in touch with us<\/a>!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>As the festival season draws to a close, we ramp up our location catering efforts across a number of TV and film projects.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":13886,"featured_media":9344,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[29],"tags":[309,307,310,306,308],"class_list":["post-9342","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-film-tv-location","tag-film-catering","tag-location-catering","tag-movie-catering","tag-tv-and-film","tag-tv-catering"],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.5 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Blockbusters: TV and film catering takes centre stage - Red Radish<\/title>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/blockbusters-festivals-make-way-as-tv-and-film-catering-takes-centre-stage\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_GB\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Blockbusters: TV and film catering takes centre stage - Red Radish\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"As the festival season draws to a close, we ramp up our location catering efforts across a number of TV and film projects.\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https:\/\/www.red-radish.com\/blockbusters-festivals-make-way-as-tv-and-film-catering-takes-centre-stage\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"Red Radish\" \/>\n<meta property=\"article:pu